dct_description_sm: In upper margin: Meyer's Handatlas. No. 35. Inset: Umgebung von Amsterdam. Includes profiles of 14 buildings with title: Grössen-Verhältniss der Haupt-Gebäude von Amsterdam. Probably issued in: Meyers grosser Hand-Atlas über alle Theile der Erde. Hildburghausen : Bibliographisches Institut, 1843-1860.
